title: American Horror Story: Double Feature | Opening Title - Season 10 Ep. 1 Highlight | FX
author: FX Networks
comment: The opening title sequence is here.
It feels so good to see Lily Rabe and Frances Conroy in the opening credits again 😭
The fact that the Same creaking gate sound was also in asylum that definitely means part 2 with the alien creatures has a crossover written all over it 😩
Did anyone else notice they used ‘X’ instead of ‘Red Tide’ like on the show? Also, the font size seems to be larger
